race.comment: Good contest. SHE'S TERNACIOUS (9) made quite the return here last month when rattling home to score with a bit in hand over this trip. Kept fresh with 34 days and is drawn kinder. Can repeat the dose over a favoured journey. COPPER BULLET (10) returns over a winning trip and looks to have come on nicely during the break, stripping fitter for a handy trial here in readiness. Gets the key booking of Toeroek and is well placed to kick the prep off on the right note. RIGHT OF VETO (8) returns and has been readied for this with two strong hitouts. Is drawn to get all the favours and can make a bright start to the campaign. BRISEIS ECLIPSE (12) has been ticking along nicely and should be sharpened by the blinkers. Can run a big race.
